#: ../../docs/classes/class_range.rst:16
msgid "Abstract base class for range-based controls."
msgstr "基于范围的控件的抽象基类。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_range.rst:19
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_range.rst:21
msgid ""
"Range is a base class for :ref:`Control <class_Control>` nodes that "
"change a floating-point *value* between a *minimum* and a *maximum*, "
"using *step* and *page*, for example a :ref:`ScrollBar "
"<class_ScrollBar>`."
msgstr ""
"对于使用 ``step`` 和 ``page``，在一个最小值 ``minimum`` 和一个最大值 ``maximum`` 之间，更改一个浮点值"
" ``value`` 的 :ref:`Control <class_Control>` 节点，例如一个 :ref:`ScrollBar "
"<class_ScrollBar>`，这是它们的一个基本类。"

